body.description: Get ready for your next holiday with the Intrepid collection by IT Luggage. Our specially developed base gives the suitcase a strong structure and added stability alongside a lightweight trolley system which helps to reduce weight, travelling has never been made easier. The 8-wheel spinner system gives superior mobility so you can navigate your journey seamlessly. If you need to bring back a holiday souvenir the expandability will give you that extra bit of space to get it home. The spacious front pocket means that any travel essentials are easily accessible while the interior mesh pocket means you can keep your items organized. Make travel exciting with the Intrepid collection by IT Luggage.

reviews.reviewText: Tons of scratches all over and residual glue. Cheaply made. Handle took force to get it to extend at first.As of writing this, I believe this is the last roller bag available that fits under the aisle on SouthWest flights. I'll test it out in a few days and maybe update.Update:It fits SouthWest narrow aisle underseat and fits in Frontiers personal item check bin if you absolutely cram the wheels
